{
  "chapter": 43,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述李密瓦岗军大败隋将刘长恭，声威大振。寇仲与徐子陵在翟让府中与俏婢楚楚嬉戏玩雪，寇仲对楚楚心生爱慕。大龙头翟让召见二人，表面询问其师承来历，实则因二人目睹其与怪人密会之事而欲杀人灭口。翟让骤然出手重伤二人，但自身内伤迸发倒地。二人借长生诀寒热真气互疗，寒热同流竟达到小成境界，功力倍增。寇仲机智骗过王儒信，携徐子陵赶往翟娇处寻找素素，计划借义气山势力逃离翟让府。章末翟娇被诱离，二人挟起素素欲逃，却发现门口出现异样。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这个妞儿逗得我忍不住了，横竖翟娇不介意我勾她的婢子，若我弄她上手，来个一夕之情，你不反对吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若她有了孩子怎办？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不会这么容易吧！人家成亲多年，很多仍是末有孩子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你自己想着辫吧！但对方是良家妇女，你绝不可始乱终弃。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中了，中了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "兄弟说得对，但亲亲嘴摸摸脸蛋也可以吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁给我拿到，就罚亲个嘴儿。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大龙头回来了，要立即见你们。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_ru_xin",
      "speaker_name": "王儒信",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "在下王儒信，任司马之职，两位小兄弟请随王某来，屠总管可以回去了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_ru_xin",
      "speaker_name": "王儒信",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大龙头在等候你们，两位请自行进去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_rang",
      "speaker_name": "翟让",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们见过我吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_rang",
      "text": "那时我们躲在梁柱上，不敢观看，兼之大龙头又来去如风，所以见不到大龙头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhai_rang",
      "text": "那是事后听得祖君彦和那藏在箱内的怪人说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_rang",
      "speaker_name": "翟让",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你们看到那个怪人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_rang",
      "text": "只看了一眼，他身形雄伟，比祖君彦至少高出半个头，不过由于他戴了面具，所以不知他是甚么模样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_rang",
      "speaker_name": "翟让",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "他的声音是怎样的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_rang",
      "text": "非常柔和好听，说完时好像仍有馀音的样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_rang",
      "speaker_name": "翟让",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你两人究竟是何家何派，为何内功如此怪异，竟能瞒过那怪人和我的耳目。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_rang",
      "text": "原来那曰遇到的真是大龙头。大龙头真厉害，那怪人还说已伤了你呢！原来只是在吹人气。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_rang",
      "speaker_name": "翟让",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们还未答我的问题。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhai_rang",
      "text": "我们的武功是娘教的，不过娘已死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_rang",
      "speaker_name": "翟让",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_rang",
      "text": "你……你干甚么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_rang",
      "speaker_name": "翟让",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "闭嘴！一切只能怪你们知道了不该知道的事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "要死就死在一块儿吧！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "快运功！我去引开他。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_rang",
      "speaker_name": "翟让",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "就让翟某人完成你们的心愿吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "要不要先干掉这忘恩负义的家伙呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那样素姐定不会原谅我们，嘿！你的真气冷得我真舒服，奇怪！为何我的天灵盖像给打开了般，不住有冷流涌入，舌尖又甜丝丝的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我的涌泉穴何尝不是热腾腾，来！快起来，我们去找素姐。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "外面那么多人，怎辫好呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "看来他们并不知道这里发生了甚么事，随机应变好了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_ru_xin",
      "text": "大龙头听了我们的故事后，才知原先误会了。但又带来他新的烦恼，所以叫我们出来，他要静静思想，吩咐任何人都不得进去打断他的思路。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "最好是能和素姐偷偷离开，立即去黛青院找义气山所说的佩佩，否则走迟半步也可能会给人分尸。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我感到功力倍增，说不定可跳过城墙，不过带着素姐，又没甚么把握了。说实话，到现在我仍不相信义气山真有义气。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们是事急马行田，先借义气山来过桥，过桥后是否抽板，那时再斟酌好了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "家将",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小姐唤你们来吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_jia_jiang",
      "text": "若不是她的命令，你肯去见她吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_chu_chu",
      "text": "美人儿你好，素姐在哪里呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "又不是来找我，人家怎知道呢！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_chu",
      "speaker_name": "楚楚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "素姐正在侍候小姐呢！呆子！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹在弄甚么鬼的，说不了两句就要见你那两个小鬼头，我不是已把事情告诉了他吗？他怎也该让我在场听听的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "大龙头请小姐前去见他，还说有礼物要送给小姐呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "不要问，若现在不离开这裹，恐怕永远都没机会了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    }
  ],
